{"tid":2160310,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"批鬥完, 有乜得着? 拎子彈, 許智峯大公單嘢潛晒底","createTime":"2020-08-17T00:22:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-17T14:01:46.000Z","uid":123774,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e21832fca359216cc08c1396f5dab00530746143","tid":2160310,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T00:22:36.000Z","msg":"講清楚事實 唔幫襯就夠<br />\n鋪天蓋地咁去批鬥 有冇得着?<br />\n等睇東周刊文匯叫小鳳姐<br />\n話黃色經濟圈係吸血圈?!<br />\n<br />\n洗走左許智峯比國安大公跟蹤單野<br />\n記協都識得叫大公出嚟開中外記招<br />\n係好幾回鞏固國際戰線<br />\n建立支共國安扮記者呢個事實基礎<br />\n但成單嘢沉晒底<br />\n<br />\n渣哥係垃圾<br />\n但成件事小題大做<br />\n幫垃圾去洗走有用嘅嘢<br />\n你比垃圾更垃圾<br />\n<br />\n唔該清醒下 唔好沉迷內鬥<br />\n都唔好俾PR帶風"},{"pid":"6a1b8700c9ed55ca2860f3662e841ffc4a0c5637","tid":2160310,"uid":123774,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T00:25:23.000Z","msg":"對手逼到你埋牆角 仲沉迷批鬥 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"602f25c18efcdcb1c2581acc85e052a5316d1d8e","tid":2160310,"uid":235535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T00:31:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fdb02be6f393ceecbb1924feca73eb2955d7f56b","tid":2160310,"uid":51820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T00:40:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"40614b7beae95572d567242e3f1cb04c88a28378","tid":2160310,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T01:16:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9be3861a734bf1336baffd8e0104eeb3b28e5905","tid":2160310,"uid":171313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T01:17:49.000Z","msg":"國安出動<br />\n黑警龜縮"},{"pid":"7c327fd8b3b4c90edcb242ccf782662c93d6c3c4","tid":2160310,"uid":166080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T01:19:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0883d34f678a17c660